    {
      "name": "A Favor Repaid",
      "description": "Gorou receives the following DMG Bonuses to his attacks based on his DEF:\n· Inuzaka All-Round Defense: Skill DMG increased by 156% of DEF\n· Juuga: Forward Unto Victory: Skill DMG and Crystal Collapse DMG increased by 15.6% of DEF",
